# Agent Foreman Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and customize as needed
# Can also be placed at ~/.agent-foreman.env for global settings

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AGENT CONFIGURATION
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Configure which AI agents to use and their priority order
# - Order determines priority: first agent is tried first
# - Only listed agents are enabled (others are ignored even if installed)
# - Valid agent names: claude, codex, gemini
# - Default: codex,gemini,claude
#
# Examples:
#   AGENT_FOREMAN_AGENTS=claude              # Only use Claude
#   AGENT_FOREMAN_AGENTS=claude,gemini       # Prefer Claude, Gemini as fallback
#   AGENT_FOREMAN_AGENTS=codex,gemini,claude # Default order (explicit)
#
# AGENT_FOREMAN_AGENTS=codex,gemini,claude

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TIMEOUT CONFIGURATION
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# All timeout values are in milliseconds
#
# IMPORTANT: Most operations have NO DEFAULT TIMEOUT - they wait for completion.
# This ensures critical operations complete successfully regardless of:
# - Project size and complexity
# - AI model response time
# - Network conditions
#
# Only bounded operations (document merging) have default timeouts.
# You can SET a timeout for any operation if needed (e.g., CI environments).

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NO TIMEOUT BY DEFAULT (wait for completion)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Project survey/scan - AI explores entire codebase (default: no timeout)
# Critical operation that must complete. Set a timeout only if needed.
# AGENT_FOREMAN_TIMEOUT_SCAN=900000

# Generate features from existing ARCHITECTURE.md (default: no timeout)
# Critical initialization path - same importance as scan.
# AGENT_FOREMAN_TIMEOUT_ANALYZE=300000

# Generate features from goal description (default: no timeout)
# Critical initialization path for new projects.
# AGENT_FOREMAN_TIMEOUT_GOAL=300000

# AI verification of feature completion (default: no timeout)
# Includes running tests/builds which can take very long.
# AGENT_FOREMAN_TIMEOUT_VERIFY=600000

# AI capability discovery (default: no timeout)
# Must complete for correct project detection.
# AGENT_FOREMAN_TIMEOUT_CAPABILITY=300000

# Global default for any AI agent call (default: no timeout)
# Safe fallback - let operations complete.
# AGENT_FOREMAN_TIMEOUT_DEFAULT=600000

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WITH TIMEOUT BY DEFAULT (bounded operations)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Merge init.sh script with AI (default: 300000 = 5 minutes)
# Bounded operation: Script merging has predictable scope.
# AGENT_FOREMAN_TIMEOUT_MERGE_INIT=300000

# Merge CLAUDE.md with AI (default: 300000 = 5 minutes)
# Bounded operation: Document merging has predictable scope.
# AGENT_FOREMAN_TIMEOUT_MERGE_CLAUDE=300000
